    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This collector-grade Mazda RX-7 FD is a masterclass in 90s JDM engineering. At its heart is the 13B-REW rotary engine, featuring a flawlessly maintained sequential twin-turbocharger system that provides a seamless transition throughout the power band. The chassis retains its original torsional rigidity, paired with a lightweight double-wishbone suspension and a Torsen limited-slip differential for surgical turn-in and balance. This example is mechanically impeccable, with pristine apex seal compression and an untouched OEM vacuum line configuration, ensuring the high-revving, longitudinal agility that defined the FD3S. A rare opportunity for the purist seeking unadulterated rotary performance in showroom condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
