    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car is in showroom condition, having been stored in a climate-controlled garage and protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that highlights its flawless, mirror-finish paint. There are absolutely no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. The interior is equally pristine; the premium leather remains supple with no signs of wear on the bolsters, and the cabin retains its original factory scent. Every technological feature\u2014from the advanced infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has been serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships, with a complete digital and physical service history included. Recently fitted with a fresh set of Michelin Pilot Sport tires and having just undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection, this vehicle needs nothing but a new home. This is a rare find for a buyer who demands the highest standard of quality and performance.",
